description:
This is a 20 minute workout called '20 MIN hourglass full body pilates workout // no equipment // beginner friendly' from the channel Lidia Mera.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Masterclass Workout and The Progression Quest vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.
